fmiModelDescription.description: Demonstrates the usage of a Continuous.LimPID controller

Item.name: NoInit
Item.description: No initialization (start values are used as guess values with fixed=false)

Item.name: SteadyState
Item.description: Steady state initialization (derivatives of states are zero)

Item.name: InitialOutput
Item.description: Initialization with initial outputs (and steady state of the states if possible)

Item.name: UpperLimit
Item.description: Simplified model fixed at upper limit

Item.name: LowerLimit
Item.description: Simplified model fixed at lower limit

Data.equation: kinematicPTP.sdd = (if time < kinematicPTP.startTime then 0 else (if kinematicPTP.noWphase then (if time < kinematicPTP.Ta1+kinematicPTP.startTime then kinematicPTP.sdd_max else (if time < kinematicPTP.Te+kinematicPTP.startTime then -kinematicPTP.sdd_max else 0)) else (if time < kinematicPTP.Ta2+kinematicPTP.startTime then kinematicPTP.sdd_max else (if time < kinematicPTP.Tv+kinematicPTP.startTime then 0 else (if time < kinematicPTP.Te+kinematicPTP.startTime then -kinematicPTP.sdd_max else 0)))));
PI.limiter.y = smooth(0, (if PI.limiter.u > PI.limiter.uMax then PI.limiter.uMax else (if PI.limiter.u < PI.limiter.uMin then PI.limiter.uMin else PI.limiter.u)));

ScalarVariable.name: PI.Ni
ScalarVariable.description: Ni*Ti is time constant of anti-windup compensation

ScalarVariable.name: PI.Nd
ScalarVariable.description: The higher Nd, the more ideal the derivative block

ScalarVariable.name: PI.initType
ScalarVariable.description: Type of initialization (1: no init, 2: steady state, 3: initial state, 4: initial output)

ScalarVariable.name: PI.xi_start
ScalarVariable.description: Initial or guess value for integrator output (= integrator state)

ScalarVariable.name: PI.xd_start
ScalarVariable.description: Initial or guess value for state of derivative block

ScalarVariable.name: PI.strict
ScalarVariable.description: = true, if strict limits with noEvent(..)

ScalarVariable.name: PI.P.k
ScalarVariable.description: Gain value multiplied with input signal

ScalarVariable.name: PI.gainPID.k
ScalarVariable.description: Gain value multiplied with input signal

ScalarVariable.name: PI.limiter.strict
ScalarVariable.description: = true, if strict limits with noEvent(..)

ScalarVariable.name: PI.I.initType
ScalarVariable.description: Type of initialization (1: no init, 2: steady state, 3,4: initial output)

ScalarVariable.name: PI.I.y_start
ScalarVariable.description: Initial or guess value of output (= state)

ScalarVariable.name: PI.gainTrack.k
ScalarVariable.description: Gain value multiplied with input signal

ScalarVariable.name: inertia1.w
ScalarVariable.description: Absolute angular velocity of component (= der(phi))

ScalarVariable.name: der(inertia1.w)
ScalarVariable.description: der(Absolute angular velocity of component (= der(phi)))

ScalarVariable.name: inertia1.a
ScalarVariable.description: Absolute angular acceleration of component (= der(w))

ScalarVariable.name: spring.phi_nominal
ScalarVariable.description: Nominal value of phi_rel (used for scaling)

ScalarVariable.name: spring.lossPower
ScalarVariable.description: Loss power leaving component via heatPort (> 0, if heat is flowing out of component)

ScalarVariable.name: inertia2.w
ScalarVariable.description: Absolute angular velocity of component (= der(phi))

ScalarVariable.name: der(inertia2.w)
ScalarVariable.description: der(Absolute angular velocity of component (= der(phi)))

ScalarVariable.name: inertia2.a
ScalarVariable.description: Absolute angular acceleration of component (= der(w))

ScalarVariable.name: kinematicPTP.startTime
ScalarVariable.description: Time instant at which movement starts

ScalarVariable.name: integrator.initType
ScalarVariable.description: Type of initialization (1: no init, 2: steady state, 3,4: initial output)

ScalarVariable.name: integrator.y_start
ScalarVariable.description: Initial or guess value of output (= state)

ScalarVariable.name: speedSensor.w
ScalarVariable.description: Absolute angular velocity of flange as output signal

ScalarVariable.name: loadTorque.phi
ScalarVariable.description: Angle of flange with respect to support (= flange.phi - support.phi)

ScalarVariable.description: der(Angle of flange with respect to support (= flange.phi - support.phi))

ScalarVariable.name: loadTorque.tau_constant
ScalarVariable.description: Constant torque (if negative, torque is acting as load in positive direction of rotation)

ScalarVariable.name: loadTorque.w
